---
title: One-Pot Bacon, Mushroom & Leek Fusilli with Parmesan Cheese & Parsley
description: If you have your favourite pair of slippers handy, we suggest putting them because a bowl of creamy fusilli is how we’re winding
down for the day. Hum in bliss when you taste the mushrooms, leek and bacon in the sauce and with only one pot it’s a dinner with no
fuss and a whole lot of comfort.
